DOC.brief_summary: Volunteers receive one injection IMD1 basic of correction of nasolabial folds and are followed-up for up to 36 weeks.
DOC.brief_title: Hyaluronic Acid Filler IMD1 Basic for Correction of Nasolabial Folds
DOC.criteria: main inclusion criteria: severity rating scale grade 3 or 4 main exclusion criterion: other nasolabial fold corrections within 6 months prior to study entry
